0workplace%20that%20just%20won't%20love%20you%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20became%20an%20account%20manager%20in%20the%20software%20development%20space%2C%20I%20specifically%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flazy-girl-job-trend-tiktok-explained-defending-low-stress-work-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echose%20a%20job%20I%20could%20quiet%20quit%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20give%20my%20entire%20body%20and%20soul%20to%20a%20company%20%E2%80%94%20I%20%3Cspan%3Epurposefully%20chose%20a%20job%20where%20I%20wasn't%20constantly%20challenged%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20showed%20up%20to%20my%20job%20and%20did%20what%20I%20was%20required%20to%20do%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20show%20initiative%20to%20push%20myself%20beyond%20that.%20I%20didn't%20take%20on%20extra%20responsibilities%20or%20try%20to%20prove%20myself%20to%20chase%20an%20ever-elusive%20raise%20that%20I%20felt%20would%20be%20held%20just%20out%20of%20my%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20spent%20over%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20quiet%20quitting%20my%20software%20job%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20great%20for%20me.%20I%20didn't%20live%20for%20my%20work%3B%20I%20worked%20to%20be%20able%20to%20live.%20I%20didn't%20go%20to%20happy%20hours%2C%20take%20on%20extra%20projects%2C%20or%20change%20my%20life%20to%20better%20fit%20myself%20to%20the%20company.%20I%20just%20spent%20that%20time%20doing%20the%20work%20I%20was%20being%20paid%20to%20do%20%E2%80%94%20another%20term%20for%20this%20is%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-act-your-wage-quiet-quit-work-less-get-paid-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eacting%20your%20wage%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20eventually%20left%20that%20position%20when%20I%20was%20asked%20to%20work%20more%20without%20being%20given%20a%20pay%20raise.%20At%20that%20point%2C%20my%20business%20and%20my%20work%20as%20a%20content%20creator%20was%20starting%20to%20blow%20