2%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20into%20an%20Airbnb%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20moved%20from%20Florida%20to%20Alaska.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20I%20had%20this%20idea%20of%20starting%20a%20flight%20school%20where%20my%20students%20could%20go%20up%20in%20a%20small%20airplane%20and%20learn%20to%20fly.%20I%20had%20a%20big%20vision%20for%20it.%20I%20wanted%20to%20have%20a%20proper%20runway%20and%20cabins%20for%20them%20to%20live%20in%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20stop%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20thinking%2C%20instead%20of%20cabins%2C%20what%20if%20my%20students%20could%20live%20in%20an%20airplane%3F%20I%20knew%20that%20would%20be%20much%20cooler.%20I%20also%20knew%20when%20my%20students%20weren't%20staying%20in%20it%2C%20it%20would%20be%20a%20great%20Airbnb.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflight-instructor-alaska-cargo-planes-airbnb-school-accommodation-photos-2023-4%5C%22%3EMy%20airplane%20house%20idea%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20big%2C%20and%20overboard%2C%20but%20my%20ideas%20usually%20are.%20In%202022%2C%20I%20bought%20a%20Douglas%20DC-6%20from%201956%20which%20I%20now%20rent%20out%20on%20Airbnb.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221388%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20exterior%20of%20Kotwicki's%20airplane%20conversion.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652971186561dd877e7a31fb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221041%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20exterior%20of%20Kotwicki's%20airplane%20conversion.%3Cp%3EJon%20Kotwicki%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EBuying%20an%20airplane%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20for%20an%20airplane%20to%20convert%20wasn't%20easy.%20Usually%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-the-air-force-recycles-planes-2012-7%5C%22%3E%20old%20airplanes%20are%20sold%20off%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20scrap%20companies%20for%20recycling.%20They're%20then%20crushed%20into%20beer%20cans.%20I%20spent%20a%20good%20six%20months%20reaching%20out%20to%20these%20companies%20and%20calling%20everyone%20I%20knew%20before%20finally%20finding%20a%20plane%20available%20for%20purchase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ended%20up%20buying%20a%201956%20Douglas%20DC-6.%20It%20was%20originally%20used%20for%20hauling%20cargo%20and%20fuel%20around%20Alaska%2C%20and%20to%20me%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20the%20perfect%20conversion.%20After%20I%20bought%20the%20plane%20the%20next%20challenge%20was%20getting%20it%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ETransporting%20an%20airplane%20that%20can't%20fly%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOld%20airplanes%20are%20fairly%20cheap%20to%20buy.%20For%20reference%2C%20the%20plane%20I%20bought%20can%20sometimes%20be%20as%20low%20as%20%2410%2C000%20for%20parts%20and%20can%20go%20up%20to%20%24250%2C000.%20Now%2C%20transporting%20an%20airplane%20can%20be%20expensive.%20Between%20buying%20and%20transporting%20the%20plane%2C%20it%20cost%20us%20just%20over%20%24100%2C000.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20then%20left%20with%20a%20104-foot-long%2C%20and%20117-foot-wide%20airplane%20to%20move.%20To%20move%20it%2C%20my%20girlfriend%2C%20buddy%2C%20and%20I%20went%20to%20Fairhaven%2C%20Alaska%2C%20where%20the%20plane%20was%20located%20and%20began%20to%20disassemble%20it.%20We%20spent%20four%20days%20taking%20the%20plane%20apart%20and%20it%20took%20us%20a%20good%2016%20hours%20each%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20unbolted%20the%20plane%2C%20and%20cut%20off%20the%20wings%20to%20make%20it%20smaller%20for%20transport.%20Then%20we%20used%20cranes%20and%20forklifts%20to%20place%20the%20plane%20parts%20onto%20separate%20trailers.%20One%20of%20our%20trailers%20was%2093%20feet%20long.%20We%20drove%20the%20trailers%20350%20miles%20to%20our%20property%20in%20Wasilla%2C%20Alaska.%20Then%20it%20was%20time%20to%20place%20it%20back%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221432%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20living%20space%20in%20Kotwicki's%20airplane%20conversion.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65296f156561dd877e7a2dfe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221074%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20living%20space%20in%20Kotwicki's%20airplane%20conversion.%3Cp%3EJon%20Kotwicki%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3ETurning%20an%20airplane%20into%20a%20house%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20I%20started%20the%20conversion%20process%2C%20I%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20easy%20because%20the%20plane%20already%20had%20walls%20and%20was%20completely%20enclosed%20like%20a%20house.%20But%20it%20wasn't%20easy.%20It%20took%20me%20five%20months%20to%20finish%20the%20conversion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20a%20normal%20house%2C%20we%20were%20building%20in%20an%20aluminum%20tin%20can.%20This%20meant%20we%20needed%20to%20find%20different%20ways%20to%20insulate%20the%20plane%2C%20and%20manage%20the%20moisture%20and%20the%20airflow.%20We%20also%20needed%20to%20heat%20the%20plane.%20Here%20in%20Alaska%2C%20we%20don't%20have%20natural%20gas.%20Instead%2C%20we%20usually%20heat%20our%20homes%20with%20wood%20or%20oil.%20In%20our%20airplane%2C%20we%20have%20an%20oil%20boiler%20in%20the%20tail%20area.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20plumbing%2C%20the%20plane%20has%20its%20own%20water%20supply%20and%20septic%20system.%20When%20building%20the%20bathroom%2C%20we%20didn't%20want%20our%20space%20to%20have%20an%20average%20airplane%20sink%2C%20where%20you%20get%20only%20a%20trickle%20of%20water.%20Instead%2C%20we%20made%20sure%20the%20plane%20got%20its%20own%20pressure%20tank%20allowing%20our%20guests%20to%20take%20normal%20showers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20conversion%2C%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20trial%20and%20error%2C%20throwing%20away%20wasted%20materials%2C%20and%20rebuilding.%20It%20was%20a%20long%20hard%20process%2C%20but%20our%20plane%20came%20out%20better%20than%20I%20ever%20could%20have%20imagined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221425%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20airplane%20conversion%20has%20two%20bedrooms.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65296fd06561dd877e7a2f46%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221069%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20airplane%20conversion%20has%20two%20bedrooms.%3Cp%3EJon%20Kotwicki%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20airplane%20sleeps%20six%20people%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plane%20has%20a%20master%20bedroom%20with%20a%20king%20size%20bed%20and%20a%20guest%20room%20with%20a%20queen%20size%20bed.%20We%20also%20have%20a%20sofa%20bed%20in%20the%20living%20room%2C%20allowing%20the%20plane%20to%20sleep%20six%20people.%20Since%20it's%20an%20airplane%2C%20the%20rooms%20are%20narrow%20and%20they%20measure%20about%20nine%20feet%20wide.%20In%20comparison%2C%20an%20average%20room%20might%20be%20about%2012%20feet.%20There's%20also%20a%20bathroom%20with%20a%20fully%20tiled%20shower%20and%20a%20toilet.%20As%20for%20the%20kitchen%2C%20it%20comes%20with%20a%20regular%20sink%2C%20refrigerator%2C%20freezer%2C%20a%20little%20toaster%20oven%2C%20microwave%2C%20and%20all%20of%20your%20basics%20for%20cooking.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221423%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20bathroom%20Kotwicki's%20airplane%20conversion.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65296f6d6561dd877e7a2e99%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221067%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bathroom%20in%20Kotwicki's%20airplane%20conversion.%3Cp%3EJon%20Kotwicki%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20now%20rent%20out%20the%20airplane%20house%20on%20Airbnb%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20originally%20made%20the%20airplane%20house%20for%20my%20students%2C%20but%20I%20also%20started%20renting%20it%20out%20on%20Airbnb%20in%20September%20starting%20at%20%24200%20a%20night.%20It%20can%20go%20up%20to%20%24700%20a%20night%20based%20on%20the%20season.%20Students%20travel%20from%20all%20over%20the%20country%20for%20their%20training%20with%20us%20and%20they%20need%20accommodation%2C%20so%20we%20provide%20it%20here%20on%20site.%20The%20accommodation%20is%20included%20in%20their%20training%20package.%20Either%20way%2C%20when%20people%20pull%20up%20to%20the%20Airplane%20house%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20I%20love%20seeing%20their%20reactions.%20They're%20always%20so%20blown%20away%20by%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20here%2C%20you%20first%20drive%20down%20one%20long%20runway.%20Then%2C%20as%20you%20come%20out%20from%20around%20the%20trees%2C%C2%A0%20you%20see%20the%20giant%20airplane%20house.%20My%20favorite%20reaction%20was%20when%20a%20couple%20brought%20their%20two%20kids.%20They%20were%20little%20girls%2C%20approximately%20ages%20four%20and%20six%2C%20and%20it%20was%20just%20the%20biggest%20surprise%20to%20them.%20They%20were%20so%20excited.%20They%20ran%20up%20and%20down%20the%20entire%20airplane%2C%20full%20sprint%20back%20and%20forth%2C%20from%20the%20cockpit%20to%20the%20master%20bedroom.%20To%20me%2C%20those%20reactions%20are%20the%20best%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221432%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20living%20space%20in%20Kotwicki's%20airplane%20conversion.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65296f156561dd877e7a2dfe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221074%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20living%20space%20in%20Kotwicki's%20airplane%20conversion.%3Cp%3EJon%20Kotwicki%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMoving%20forward%2C%20I'll%20soon%20be%20putting%20a%20hot%20tub%20on%20the%20wing%20tip.%20I'm%20waiting%20for%20spring%20to%20do%20that%20project.%20I%20figure%20no%20one%20will%20want%20to%20use%20it%20in%20the%20winter%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20since%20it%20gets%2020%20degrees%20below%20zero%20here.%20Once%20the%20hot%20tub%20is%20done%2C%20I%20know%20it%20will%20be%20a%20big%20attraction%20for%20those%20who%20rent%20from%20us.%20Finally%2C%20I%20am%20working%20on%20anot