p%3EThe%20Amazon%20Labor%20Union%20was%20founded%20in%202021%20by%20a%20group%20of%20labor%20activists%2C%20called%20the%20Congress%20of%20Essential%20Workers.%20The%20group%2C%20founded%20by%20Smalls%2C%20Jordan%20Flowers%2C%20Gerald%20Bryson%2C%20and%20Derrick%20Palmer%2C%20is%20a%20collective%20of%20essential%20workers%2C%20including%20servers%2C%20warehouse%20workers%2C%20teachers%2C%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmalls%2C%20a%20former%20Amazon%20employee%2C%20was%20fired%20by%20the%20company%20after%20organizing%20a%20protest%20over%20COVID%20safety%20concerns.%20In%20April%202022%2C%20Amazon%20workers%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-work-at-the-amazon-warehouse-unionizing-in-staten-island-2021-12%5C%22%3EJFK8%20Fulfillment%20Center%20in%20Staten%20Island%3C%2Fa%3E%20voted%20to%20create%20the%20first%20Amazon%20Labor%20Union.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20aim%20of%20the%20Amazon%20Labor%20Union%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Amazon%20Labor%20Union%20is%20focused%20on%20better%20pay%2C%20better%20benefits%2C%20and%20better%20working%20conditions%20for%20Amazon%20workers.%20The%20union%20called%20for%20hourly%20wages%20to%20increase%20to%20at%20least%20%2430%20an%20hour%20and%20more%20paid%20breaks%20and%20time%20off.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20don't%20Amazon%20workers%20want%20to%20be%20in%20a%20union%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20workers%20in%20Staten%20Island%20voted%20to%20unionize%20in%202022.%20But%2C%20the%20move%20followed%20a%20failed%20union%20vote%20at%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-union-vote-fails-bessemer-alabama-warehouse-workers-2021-4%5C%22%3EAmazon%20warehouse%20in%20Bessemer%2C%20Alabama%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%202021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorkers%20at%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworkers-first-union-push-at-amazon-retail-store-want-25hr-2022-3%5C%22%3EAmazon%20Fres