se-fighter-jets-spook-canadian-plane-on-un-mission%2Famp_articleshow%2F104491668.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Are%20Supreme%20Court's%20Directives%20To%20Centre%2C%20States%20On%20Queer%20Rights%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20directed%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20state%20governments%20to%20ensure%20that%20queer%20people%20are%20not%20discriminated%20against%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20their%20sexual%20orientation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDirecting%20the%20government%20to%20sentisize%20the%20public%20about%20queer%20rights%20and%20set%20up%20a%20hotline%20for%20them%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20said%20that%20queer%20is%20a%20natural%20phenomenon%20known%20for%20ages%2C%20and%20is%20neither%20urban%20nor%20elitist.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BQueerness%20is%20neither%20urban%20nor%20elitist.%20However%2C%20we%20do%20not%20agree%20with%20the%20directions%20issued%20by%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20directed%20the%20police%20to%20conduct%20a%20preliminary%20enquiry%20before%20registering%20a%20First%20Information%20Report%20or%20FIR%20against%20a%20queer%20couple%20over%20their%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20shall%20be%20no%20harassment%20to%20queer%20community%20by%20summoning%20them%20to%20police%20station%20solely%20to%20enquire%20about%20their%20sexual%20identity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20people%20of%20the%20queer%20community%20can't%20be%20forced%20to%20return%20to%20their%20families%20or%20to%20undergo%20any%20hormonal%20therapy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20asked%20the%20government%20to%20ensure%20that%20inter-sex%20children%20are%20not%20forced%20for%20sex%20change%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20five-judge%20Constitution%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20refused%20to%20grant%20legal%20recognition%20to%20same-sex%20marriages.%20The%20Chief%20Justice%20said