hts%20for%20queer%20couples.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20judges%20asked%20the%20centre%20to%20proceed%20with%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20committee%20to%20address%20practical%20concerns%20of%20same-sex%20couples%2C%20such%20as%20getting%20ration%20cards%2C%20pension%2C%20gratuity%20and%20succession%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20centre%20had%20on%20May%203%20told%20the%20court%20that%20it%20plans%20to%20form%20a%20committee%20headed%20by%20a%20cabinet%20secretary%20to%20explore%20administrative%20solution%20to%20problems%20faced%20by%20same-sex%20couples%20without%20delving%20into%20the%20marriage%20equality%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20gave%20a%203-2%20judgment%20on%20the%20question%20of%20adoption%20rights.%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20and%20Justice%20SK%20Kaul%20recognised%20the%20right%20of%20queer%20couples%20to%20adopt%2C%20while%20Justice%20S%20Ravindra%20Bhat%2C%20Justice%20PS%20Narasimha%20and%20Justice%20Hima%20Kohli%20disagreed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20degree%20of%20agreement%20and%20a%20degree%20of%20disagreement%20on%20how%20far%20we%20have%20to%20go.%20I%20have%20dealt%20with%20the%20issue%20of%20judicial%20review%20and%20separation%20of%20powers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChoosing%20a%20life%20partner%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20choosing%20one's%20course%20of%20life%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said.%20%26quot%3BSome%20may%20regard%20this%20as%20the%20most%20important%20decision%20of%20their%20life.%20This%20right%20goes%20to%20the%20root%20of%20the%20right%20to%20life%20and%20liberty%20under%20Article%2021%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20right%20to%20enter%20into%20union%20includes%20the%20right%20to%20choose%20one's%20partner%20and%20the%20right%20to%20recognition%20of%20that%20union.%20A%20failure%20to%20recognise%20such%20associations%20will%20result%20in%20discrimination%20against%20queer%20couples%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20right%20to%20enter%20into%20union%20cannot%20be%20restricted%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20sexual%20orientation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDisagreeing%20with%20the%20centre's%20argument%20that%20marriage%20equality%20is%20an%20urban%2C%20elite%20concept%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BQueerness%20is%20not%20urban%20elite.%20Homosexuality%20or%20queerness%20is%20not%20an%20urban%20concept%20or%20restricted%20to%20the%20upper%20classes%20of%20the%20society.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESupporting%20adoption%20rights%20for%20queer%20couples%2C%20he%20said%20there%20is%20nothing%20to%20probe%20that%20only%20heterosexual%20couples%20can%20provide%20stability%20to%20a%20child.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20material%20on%20record%20to%20prove%20that%20only%20a%20married%20heterosexual%20couple%20can%20provide%20stability%20to%20a%20child%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20Central%20Adoption%20Resource%20Authority%20%26quot%3Bexceeded%20its%20authority%26quot%3B%20in%20barring%20adoption%20by%20same-sex%20couples.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJustice%20Kaul%20agreed%20with%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20that%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20an%20anti-discrimination%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSame-sex%20relationships%20have%20been%20recognised%20from%20antiquity%2C%20not%20just%20for%20sexual%20activities%20but%20as%20relationships%20for%20emotional%20fulfilment.%20I%20have%20referred%20to%20certain%20Sufi%20traditions.%20I%20agree%20with%20the%20judgment%20of%20the%20Chief%20Justice.%20It%20is%20not%20res%20integra%20for%20a%20constitutional%20court%20to%20uphold%20the%20rights%20and%20the%20court%20has%20been%20guided%20by%20the%20constitutional%20morality%20and%20not%20social%20morality.%20These%20unions%20are%20to%20be%20recognised%20as%20a%20union%20to%20give%20partnership%20and%20love%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJustice%20Bhat%20agreed%20that%20queerness%20is%20%26quot%3Bneither%20urban%20nor%20elitist%26quot%3B%2C%20but%20added%20that%20he%20does%20not%20agree%20with%20the%20Chief%20Justice's%20directions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20judgment%20of%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20propounded%20a%20theory%20of%20a%20unified%20thread%20of%20rights%20and%20how%20lack%20of%20recognition%20violated%20rights.%20However%2C%20when%20the%20law%20is%20silence%2C%20Article%2019(1)(a)%20does%20not%20compel%20the%20State%20to%20enact%20a%20law%20to%20facilitate%20that%20expression%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJustice%20Bhat%20said%20the%20court%20cannot%20create%20a%20legal%20framework%20for%20queer%20couples%20and%20it%20is%20for%20the%20legislature%20to%20do%20as%20there%20are%20several%20aspects%20to%20be%20taken%20into%20consideration.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20issue%20of%20adoption%2C%20Justice%20Bhat%20said%20they%20disagree%20with%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20on%20the%20right%20of%20queer%20couples%20to%20adopt.%20%26quot%3BWe%20voice%20certain%20concerns.%20This%20is%20not%20to%20say%20that%20unmarried%20or%20non-heterosexual%20couples%20can't%20be%20good%20parents...%20given%20the%20objective%20of%20section%2057%2C%20the%20State%20as%20parens%20patriae%20has%20to%20explore%20all%20areas%20and%20to%20ensure%20all%20benefits%20reach%20the%20children%20at%20large%20in%20need%20of%20stable%20homes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20disagreed%20with%20Justice%20Bhat's%20approach.%20%26quot%3BMy%20learned%20brother%20acknowledges%20the%20discrimination%20against%20the%20queer%20couples%20but%20does%20not%20issue%20directions.%20I%20cannot%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20such%20an%20approach.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20judges%20agreed%20that%20the%20court%20should%20not%20try%20to%20tweak%20the%20Special%20Marriage%20Act%20as%20it%20would%20amount%20to%20encroaching%20into%20the%20legislature's%20domain.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20court%20cannot%20strike%20down%20the%20Special%20Marriage%20Act%20or%20read%20words%20into%20the%20law%20due%20to%20institutional%20limitations.%20The%20court%20cannot%20read%20words%20into%20allied%20laws%20like%20the%20Succession%20Act%20as%20it%20would%20amount%20to%20legislation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJustice%20Kaul%20agreed.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20said%20that%20the%20Special%20Marriage%20Act%20is%20violative%20of%20Article%2014.%20But%20there%20are%20interpretative%20limitations%20in%20including%20homosexual%20unions%20in%20it.%20As%20rightly%20pointed%20by%20Solicitor%20General%2C%20tinkering%20with%20Special%20Marriage%20Act%20can%20have%20a%20cascading%20effect%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697530500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2F3k0690i_pride-rally_625x300_19_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-set-up-committee-to-decide-rights-of-persons-in-queer-unions-chief-justice-4488067%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Chief%20Justice%20said%20the%20five-judge%20bench%20has%20authored%20four%20separate%20judgments%20--%20one%20by%20him%20and%20others%20by%20Justice%20SK%20Kaul%2C%20Justice%20SR%20Bhat%20and%20Justice%20PS%20Narasimha.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-set-up-committee-to-decide-rights-of-persons-in-queer-unions-chief-justice-4488067%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-set-up-committee-to-decide-rights-of-persons-in-queer-unions-chief-justice-4488067%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-set-up-committee-to-decide-rights-of-persons-in-queer-unions-chief-justice-4488067%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Aapka%20kaptaan%20jab%20dara%20hua%20nazar%20aaye...'%3A%20Moin%20criticises%20Babar%22%2C%22cont