n%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUS%20dollar%20and%20euro%20transactions%2C%20saw%20a%20sharp%20decline%20%E2%80%9Cin%20the%20same%20period%20to%2067%25%20from%20up%20to%2080%25%2C%E2%80%9D%20as%20per%20the%20Study.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUkraine%20war%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Ukraine%20war%20and%20the%20consequent%20sanctions%20on%20Russian%20oil%20have%20been%20exploited%20by%20India%20as%20it%20has%20emerged%20as%20among%20the%20top%20importers%20of%20Russian%20crude.%20For%20a%20while%2C%20it%20knocked%20off%20West%20Asia%20as%20its%20prime%20supplier.%20Reports%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-60783874%5C%22%3Ein%20the%20BBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Finteractive%2F2023%2F05%2F30%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Frussia-oil-ships-sanctions.html%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20have%20mapped%20the%20journey%20of%20Russian%20oil%20for%20India.%20This%20has%20often%20been%20seen%20as%20a%20problem%20and%20the%20ships%20carrying%20the%20oil%20termed%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdark%20fleet%E2%80%9D.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Findia-russia-oil-trade-gatik-ship-management%5C%22%3Emysterious%20Mumbai%20Company%2C%20Gatik%20Ship%20Management%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20reported%20to%20have%20been%20shipping%20large%20quantities%20of%20Russian%20oil%2C%20earlier%20this%20year.%20The%20company%2C%20having%20purchased%20more%20oil%20tankers%20than%20any%20other%20company%20since%20Russia%20invaded%20Ukraine%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20India%E2%80%99s%20imports%20of%20Russian%20crude%20were%20recently%20described%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2023%2F09%2F06%2Findia-importing-russian-oil-is-win-win-for-global-economy-says-ongc.html%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Ca%20win-win%20situation%20for%20the%20world%20economy%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20by%20the%20public%20sector%E2%80%99s%20Oil%20and%20Natural%20Gas%20Corporation%20or%20O