%20hands%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20some%20of%20the%20leaders%20even%20quit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20JD(S)%20presence%20outside%20Karnataka%20is%20limited%2C%20the%20latest%20statement%20by%20the%20Karnataka%20party%20unit%20president%20assumes%20significance%20given%20that%20it%20is%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20home%20turf.%20Ibrahim%E2%80%99s%20divergent%20views%20to%20that%20of%20the%20leadership%20indicate%20a%20possible%20split%20in%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20first%20decision%20is%20that%20the%20JD(S)%20will%20not%20go%20with%20the%20NDA.%20The%20second%20decision%20was%20a%20request%20to%20Deve%20Gowda%20that%20he%20should%20not%20give%20his%20consent%20to%20this%20alliance%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ibrahim%20told%20reporters%20after%20a%20meeting%20with%20some%20party%20leaders%20in%20Bengaluru%20on%20Monday%2C%20October%2016%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fkarnataka%2Fjds-not-joining-nda-karnataka-party-chief-contradicts-deve-gowda-hints-at-split-2728792%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20PTI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Karnataka%2C%20however%2C%20we%20still%20have%20affection%20for%20you.%20You%20are%20a%20father%20figure.%20We%20will%20tell%20him%20(Gowda)%20that%20we%20should%20not%20have%20any%20relation%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ibrahim%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20would%20be%20forming%20a%20core%20committee%2C%20which%20will%20meet%20Deve%20Gowda%20and%20convey%20the%20decision%20taken%20at%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20specifically%20if%20Gowda%20and%20Kumaraswamy%20do%20not%20agree%20with%20his%20views%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20the%20state%20president.%20I%20have%20to%20decide%20about%20my%20party%20in%20the%20state%2C%20which%20I%20will%20take.%20Already%20we%20have%20decided%20that%20we%20will%20not%20go%20with%20the%20BJP.%20What%20else%20is%20there%20more%20than%20this%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EContinuing%20further%2C%20he%20said%2C%C2%