%20to%20the%20bread%2C%20quite%20similar%20to%20Northern%20European%20breads%20like%20rye.%20Lately%2C%20we%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20fans%20who%20wait%20for%20this%20bread%20to%20be%20put%20on%20the%20menu%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EElizabeth%20says%20that%20she%20was%20able%20to%20upcycle%201%2C200%20kg%20of%20spent%20grain%20last%20financial%20year%20(2022-23)%20and%20saved%20it%20from%20being%20discarded%20as%20trash%20into%20useful%20and%20flavoursome%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20also%20comes%20with%20a%20set%20of%20challenges%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20it%20is%20a%20new%20ingredient%2C%20making%20new%20recipes%20from%20it%20was%20a%20little%20challenging.%20Most%20of%20our%20time%20goes%20into%20research%20and%20development.%20I%20have%20even%20written%20a%20handbook%20on%20how%20to%20use%20the%20spent%20grain%20to%20make%20new%20recipes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlso%2C%20not%20many%20people%20know%20about%20it%20as%20it%20is%20new%20for%20most%20of%20the%20people%20in%20India.%20Our%20main%20purpose%20is%20to%20build%20a%20conversation%20on%20upcycling%20food.%20Thankfully%2C%20I%20can%20implement%20my%20ideas%20and%20complete%20the%20circular%20loop%2C%20just%20like%20the%20brewers%20and%20bakers%20from%20the%20past%20did%20it%2C%20the%20old-fashioned%20way!%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Elizabeth%20Yorke.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697466790000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D332299%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20chef%20turned%20food%20researcher%2C%20Elizabeth%20Yorke%20upcycles%20%E2%80%98spent%20grain%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20byproduct%20in%20the%20beer%20brewing%20process%20%E2%80%94%20from%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20breweries%20into%20sustainable%20goodies.%20Last%20year%2C%20she%20saved%201%2C200%20kgs%20of%20spent%20grain%20from%20being%20discarded%20as%20trash%20into%20u