0Press%20Journal%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20also%20help%20government%20agencies%20monitor%20dropouts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20student%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Ffor-school-students-government-plans-to-roll-out-one-nation-one-id%2Farticleshow%2F104430743.cms%5C%22%3EAadhaar%20data%20will%20serve%20as%20the%20basis%20for%20their%20APAAR%20ID.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20student%E2%80%99s%20APAAR%20ID%20will%20require%20their%20parents%E2%80%99%20consent.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%E2%80%99s%20government%20has%20asked%20all%20schools%20to%20take%20consent%20from%20parents%20for%20the%20creation%20of%20students%E2%80%99%20APAAR%20IDs%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EExpress%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESchools%20have%20also%20been%20asked%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fmumbai-news%2Fnew-national-student-id-scheme-requires-parental-consent-for-student-registrations-101697311178545.html%5C%22%3Ehold%20special%20parent-teacher%20association%20meetings%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20Wednesday%20(October%2016)%20and%20Friday%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20APAAR%20IDs%20among%20parents%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%2C%20they%20will%20be%20required%20to%20mark%20each%20student%20as%20%E2%80%9Cconsented%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20consented%E2%80%9D%20in%20a%20Union%20government%20education%20database%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3EHT%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3Es%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20brief%20by%20the%20Union%20education%20ministry%20said%20that%20as%20of%20July%20this%20year%20%E2%80%93%20two%20years%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20launched%20the%20APAAR%20programme%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Feducation.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fupload_files%2Fmhrd%2Ffiles%2Fnep%2FOutcome_Document_Thematic_Sessions_ABSS_2023.pdf%5C%22%3E1.24%20crore%20APAAR%20IDs%20had%20been%20created%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20educators%20have%20voiced%20their%20apprehensions%20about%20the%20APAAR%20ID%20system%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20having%20to%20collect%20data%20for%20students%E2%80%99%20APAAR%20IDs%20was%20another%20item%20in%20an%20increasing%20list%20of%20non-academic%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSchools%20just%20completed%20work%20of%20students%E2%80%99%20Aadhaar%20card%20update%20on%20UDISE%20%5BUnified%20District%20Information%20System%20for%20Education%5D.%20Now%2C%20a%20new%20ID%20card%20is%20in%20the%20making.%20We%20also%20have%20to%20update%20each%20student%E2%80%99s%20height%2C%20weight%20and%20blood-group%20on%20UDISE.%20This%20leaves%20us%20no%20time%20to%20focus%20on%20academics%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pandurang%20Kengar%2C%20a%20member%20of%20a%20school%20principals%E2%80%99%20association%20from%20Mumbai%2C%20told%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJalindar%20Sarode%2C%20representative%20of%20Shikshak%20Bharti%2C%20told%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20teachers%20will%20turn%20into%20data%20entry%20operators%20if%20the%20government%20imposes%20new%20work%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDetails%20of%20every%20student%20is%20available%20on%20UDISE.%20Then%20why%20is%20new%20data%20required%3F%20This%20only%20poses%20additional%20burden%20on%20teachers%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20newspaper%20quoted%20Sarode%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0%3Cem%3EFree%20Press%20Journal%3C%2Fem%3E%20cited%20educators%20as%20saying%20that%20while%20the%20APAAR%20programme%20is%20voluntary%2C%20schools%20will%20be%20forced%20to%20ensure%20the%20participation%20of%20all%20stakeholders%2C%20much%20like%20Aadhaar%20verifications.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHaving%20an%20Aadhaar%20number%20has%20become%20increasingly%20necessary%20to%20access%20common%20services%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EExperts%20have%20also%20criticised%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20policy%20of%20making%20Aadhaar%20virtually%20compulsory%20for%20accessing%20some%20government%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20seen%20in%20scheme%20after%20scheme%20that%20%E2%80%98voluntary%E2%80%99%20Aadhaar-linking%20ended%20up%20reducing%20the%20number%20of%20beneficiaries%20as%20the%20government%20claimed%20that%20those%20who%20didn%E2%80%99t%20link%20it%20were%20either%20%E2%80%98ghosts%E2%80%99%2C%20when%20in%20fact%20they%20were%20very%20much%20alive%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Faadhaar-voter-id-linking-deadline%5C%22%3Eeconomist%20Reetika%20Khera%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFPJ%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20quoted%20Kishore%20Darak%2C%20a%20Maharashtra-based%20educator%2C%20as%20saying%20that%20APAAR%E2%80%99s%20linkage%20with%20Aadhaar%20makes%20it%20vulnerable%20to%20misuse%20by%20third%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLooking%20at%20the%20overall%20notion%20and%20laws%20of%20confidentiality%20in%20the%20country%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20unlikely%20that%20the%20data%20will%20remain%20safe.%20Linking%20APAAR%20with%20Aadhaar%20will%20have%20a%20direct%20effect%20of%20the%20latter%20being%20made%20mandatory.%20It%20will%20violate%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20verdict%20on%20Aadhaar%20and%20the%20Right%20to%20Education%20Act%2C%20which%20stipulates%20that%20no%20child%20can%20be%20denied%20schooling%20and%20other%20entitlements%2C%E2%80%9D%20Darak%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697453740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21211445%2FAadhaar-1200x560-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fmaharashtra-directs-schools-to-get-parental-consent-for-student-unique-ids%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Educators%20have%20voiced%20their%20apprehensions%20a