20election%20affidavit.%20This%2C%20the%20notice%20says%2C%20had%20%E2%80%9Crattled%E2%80%9D%20Dubey%20and%20so%20he%20was%20now%20making%20these%20false%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Dehadrai%2C%20the%20notice%20says%20that%20Moitra%20and%20the%20advocate%20used%20to%20be%20close%20friends%2C%20but%20had%20a%20falling%20out.%20After%20that%2C%20Dehadrai%20allegedly%20%E2%80%9Crepeatedly%20threatened%20our%20Client%20%5BMoitra%5D%20with%20several%20vile%2C%20malicious%20and%20vulgar%20messages%E2%80%9D%20and%20trespassed%20on%20her%20official%20residence%20and%20stole%20personal%20possessions%2C%20including%20Moitra%E2%80%99s%20dog.%20The%20legal%20notice%20says%20the%20dog%20was%20later%20returned.%20After%20repeated%20violations%2C%20Moitra%20had%20filed%20police%20complaints%20against%20Dehadrai.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDehadrai%20tried%20to%20get%20journalists%20to%20publish%20false%20stories%20about%20Moitra%2C%20the%20notice%20says%2C%20but%20could%20not%20convince%20anyone%20because%20of%20the%20lack%20of%20evidence%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20soon%20after%20convincing%20our%20Client%20%5BMoitra%5D%20to%20withdraw%20the%20%5Bpolice%5D%20Complaints%20dated%2025%20March%202023%20and%2023%20September%202023%2C%20Noticee%20No.%202%20%5BDehadrai%5D%20immediately%20zapped%20back%20to%20old%20ways%20and%20continued%20his%20misguided%20and%20malicious%20pursuit%20of%20vendetta%20against%20our%20Client.%20Noticee%20No.%202%20reached%20out%20to%20several%20prominent%20journalists%20and%20attempted%20to%20convince%20them%20to%20run%20stories%20based%20on%20wild%2C%20vindictive%2C%20fictitious%20and%20entirely%20imaginary%20allegations%20about%20our%20Client.%20It%20appears%20that%20no%20credible%20journalist%20responded%20to%20Noticee%20No.%202%E2%80%99s%20desperate%20attempts%20to%20malign%20our%20Client%E2%80%99s%20reputation%20basis%20unsupported%20and%20unsubstantiated%20allegations%20without%20even%20a%20shred%20of%20evidence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20journalists%20could%20not%20be%20convinced%2C%20Dehadrai%20then%20approached%20the%20BJP%20and%20Dubey%2C%20the%20notice%20states.%20Dubey%20then%20went%20on%20to%20repeat%20these%20allegations%20and%20%E2%80%9Cdid%20not%20even%20bother%20to%20conduct%20any%20due%20diligence%20of%20any%20kind%20to%20establish%20the%20veracity%20of%20the%20allegations%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNot%20only%20did%20Noticee%20No.%201%20%5BDubey%5D%20relay%2C%20endorse%20and%20exaggerate%20the%20false%2C%20baseless%20and%20per%20se%20defamatory%20allegations%20against%20our%20Client%20%5BMoitra%5D%2C%20but%20also%20proceeded%20to%20leak%20the%20same%20to%20members%20of%20the%20media.%20Noticee%20No.%201%20and%202%20%5BDehadrai%5D%20are%20both%20directly%20responsible%20for%20defaming%20and%20maligning%20the%20reputation%20and%20goodwill%20of%20our%20Client%20for%20their%20own%20respective%20personal%20and%20political%20vendettas%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20legal%20notice%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20notice%20also%20makes%20clear%20that%20Moitra%20rejects%20the%20allegations%20made%20as%20completely%20baseless%3A%20%E2%80%9COur%20Client%20has%20never%20accepted%20any%20remuneration%20or%20cash%20or%20gift%20or%20benefit%20of%20any%20kind%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20discharge%20of%20her%20duties%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Parliament%2C%20including%20but%20not%20limited%20to%2C%20the%20questions%20raised%20by%20her%20in%20Parliament%20and%20any%20suggestion%20to%20the%20contrary%20is%20vehemently%20denied%20by%20our%20Client.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20notice%20also%20says%20that%20Dubey%20and%20Dehadrai%20have%20leaked%20private%20photos%20of%20Moitra%20after%20cropping%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20notice%20calls%20upon%20Dubey%20to%20withdraw%20his%20letter%20to%20the%20speaker%20and%20all%20allegations%2C%20and%20issue%20a%20public%20apology%20to%20Moitra.%20Dehadrai%20has%20also%20been%20asked%20to%20withdraw%20the%20allegations%20in%20all%20comm