in%2Frights%2Fpalestine-solidarity-jantar-mantar-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20a%20time%20when%20empathy%20for%20one%E2%80%99s%20fellow%20citizens%20seems%20to%20have%20dipped%20to%20an%20all-time%20low%2C%20it%20was%20heartening%20to%20see%20a%20group%20of%20150%20people%20express%20solidarity%20for%20the%20suffering%20of%20millions%20in%20another%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A76%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpalestine-solidarity-jantar-mantar-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%3A%20Petrol%2C%20LPG%20Dealers%20Warn%20of%20Looming%20Crisis%20if%20Highway%20Blockades%20Continue%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13113152%2FF8LBinRaoAAaWqN.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Even%20though%20security%20advisor%20to%20the%20Manipur%20government%2C%20Kuldiep%20Singh%2C%20had%20recently%20told%20local%20media%20that%20the%20state%20police%20has%20made%20arrangements%20for%20a%20separate%20escort%20party%20for%20petroleum%20tankers%20to%20wheel%20down%20National%20Highway%2037%20without%20facing%20attack%20by%20miscreants%2C%20drivers%2C%20transporters%20and%20dealers%20associations%20of%20petrol%20pumps%20and%20LPG%20outlets%20of%20the%20valley%20areas%20came%20together%20in%20Imphal%20this%20Sunday%20to%20state%20a%20different%20ground%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENews%20reports%20quoting%20them%20states%20that%20if%20the%20state%20government%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20address%20the%20situation%20%E2%80%9Cat%20the%20earliest%E2%80%9D%2C%20there%20is%20going%20to%20be%20crisis%20situation%20for%20LPG%20and%20petrol%20supply.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifp.co.in%2Fmanipur%2Fgovernment-intervention-sought-as-oil-stock-nears-zero-at-retail-outlets%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EImphal%20Free%20Press%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9Cninety%20percent%20of%20the%20retail%20outlets%20and%20underground%20tanks%20are%20drying%20out%20(except%20for%20dead%20stock)%20and%20only%20a%20few%20retail%20outlets%20are%20having%20maximum%20stock%20which%20will%20run%20out%20in%20three%20or%20four%20days%20maximum%2C%20especially%20the%20petrol%20products.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20report%20said%20the%20meeting%20was%20jointly%20called%20by%20Drivers%E2%80%99%20Association%20of%20POL%2C%20POL%20Transport%20bulk%20LPG%20and%20petroleum%20dealers%20of%20Manipur%20where%20%E2%80%9Caggrieved%20dealers%E2%80%9D%20spoke%20of%20facing%20issues%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Csevere%20nature%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20arterial%20highway%20that%20connects%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Jiribam%20to%20the%20state%20capital%20Imphal%20through%20the%20tribal-dominated%20districts%20of%20Kangpokpi%20and%20Tamenglong.%20The%20report%20said%20those%20issues%20%E2%80%9Cinvolve%20firing%20gun%20bullets%20at%20the%20vehicles%2C%20several%20physical%20assault%20or%20harassment%20and%20rampant%20exorbitant%20extortion%20at%20multiple%20areas%20which%20is%20increasing%20day%20by%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20continuing%20strife%20between%20the%20Kuki%20and%20Meitei%20communities%20dominant%20in%20the%20hill%20and%20valley%20areas%20respectively%2C%20some%20powerful%20Kuki%20civil%20society%20organisations%20like%20Committee%20on%20Tribal%20Unity%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fmanipur-blockade-of-vital-national-highway-continues-hits-supplies-in-tribal-areas%2Farticleshow%2F102950173.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Edeclared%20an%20%E2%80%98economic%20blockade%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20highway%2C%20a%20lifeline%20of%20sorts%20for%20essential%20goods%20to%20the%20valley%20areas.%20At%20several%20times%2C%20the%20state%20government%20has%20said%20that%20it%20has%20cleared%20the%20road%20from%20such%20a%20blockade%20which%20the%20drivers%20and%2