coaching%20club.%20While%20going%20for%20a%20run%2C%20his%20marathon%20mates%20spoke%20about%20going%20cycling%20to%20Sewri%2C%20to%20see%20flamingos.%20The%20banker%20was%20pleasantly%20surprised%20when%20he%20learnt%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F128588%2Fmumbai-thane-flamingo-sanctuary-maharashtra-mangrove-cell%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflamingos%3C%2Fa%3E%20come%20to%20Mumbai%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20curiosity%20piqued%2C%20the%20bird%20lover%20cycled%20with%20his%20friends%20to%20Sewri%20the%20next%20morning.%20What%20he%20saw%20bowled%20him%20over.%20He%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20wading%20birds%20the%20first%20time%20he%20laid%20eyes%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20his%20marathon%20coach%20about%20his%20experience%20and%20was%20informed%20by%20him%20that%20there%20was%20a%20small%20lake%20behind%20the%20NRI%20complex%20residential%20area%20in%20Navi%20Mumbai%2C%20to%20which%20flamingos%20throng%20in%20thousands%20during%20the%20season%20and%20could%20be%20seen%20in%20much%20closer%20quarters%20than%20Sewri.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVidyasagar%20can%20perfectly%20recall%20that%20Saturday%20morning%20in%20March%202016%20like%20it%20was%20yesterday.%20He%20calls%20what%20he%20saw%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331893%2Fmental-health-care-therapy-counselling-affordable-startups-india-online%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98magic%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20heard%20a%20loud%20noise%20as%20we%20were%20nearing%20the%20waterbody.%20It%20was%20the%20sound%20of%20thousands%20of%20flamingos%20cackling.%20The%20rising%20sun%20painted%20the%20murky%20tidal%20waters%20and%20the%20pink%20birds%20golden.%20I%20was%20enamoured%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2047-year-old.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-